Seamus Coleman: &ldquo;Every Everton fan, every Everton player is going to want their rivals not to win, but as players we respect what they&rsquo;ve done as a team, no one can take that away from Liverpool. What they did against Barcelona was incredible.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Coleman: &ldquo;As Everton we&rsquo;ve just got to worry about ourselves and make sure our seasons improve. Let the best team win, if that&rsquo;s Liverpool or Tottenham then so be it, it&rsquo;s good for the Premier League.&rdquo;
